tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE climate_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    location VARCHAR(255),
    temperature FLOAT,
    precipitation FLOAT,
    sea_level FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE analysis (
    date DATE,
    analysis_id INT,
    temperature FLOAT,
    precipitation FLOAT,
    sea_level FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE analysis_data (
    analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    date TIMESTAMP,
    location VARCHAR(255),
    temperature DECIMAL,
    precipitation DECIMAL,
    sea_level DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE modeling_data (
    model_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    date TIMESTAMP,
    location VARCHAR(255),
    temperature DECIMAL,
    precipitation DECIMAL,
    sea_level DECIMAL
);
